  "text": "DNA extraction was carried out in the labs contributing the sorghum entries to this study, with a single representative plant providing the DNA for each accession, following a protocol described by [CITATION_1] for accessions contributed by ICRISAT and as described in [CITATION_2] for accessions contributed by CIRAD and CAAS. Extracted DNA samples were exchanged between the labs for SSR marker genotyping.",
